00:19:22,860 --> 00:19:25,460
♪ Sesat di padang gurun ♪

371
00:19:26,390 --> 00:19:28,770
♪ Saya telah mencari awak ♪

372
00:19:28,970 --> 00:19:32,210
♪ Walaupun kehancuran memenuhi mata saya ♪

373
00:19:32,580 --> 00:19:35,370
♪ Bayang-bayang terus bergoyang ♪

374
00:19:35,850 --> 00:19:38,600
♪ Phoenix melawan cahaya ♪

375
00:19:39,120 --> 00:19:41,940
♪ Telah mencari seribu batu ♪

376
00:19:42,300 --> 00:19:45,480
♪ Semakin tahun berlalu, habuk bergolak,
